
📖 Overview
The Student Registration Dashboard is a responsive web application developed using HTML, CSS, and JavaScript. It provides a simple and modern interface for managing student records. Users can add, edit, delete, and view student information through an interactive dashboard.
✨ Features
.Add new student records
.Edit existing student details
.Delete student records
.Display student data in a table
.Responsive and modern user interface
.Client-side form validation
.Easy-to-use dashboard layout
🛠️ Technologies Used
.HTML5
.CSS3
.JavaScript (ES6)
📁 Project Structure
Student-Registration-Dashboard/
├── index.html
├── style.css
├── script.js
└── README.md
🚀 How to Run
1.Download or clone this repository.
2.Open the project folder.
3.Open index.html in any modern web browser.
4.Start adding and managing student records.
🎯 Learning Objectives
.Build responsive web interfaces.
.Practice DOM manipulation.
.Implement CRUD operations using JavaScript.
.Improve front-end development skills.
📌 Future Enhancements
.Store data using Local Storage or a database.
.Add search and filter functionality.
.Export student records to PDF or Excel.
.User authentication and login system
